info.author: Jeff Whitaker
info.description:
GRIB2 is the second version of the World Meterological Organization (WMO)
standard for distributing gridded data. This module includes a python programmer
interface for reading and writing GRIB2 grids as well as command-line utilites
for listing and re-packing GRIB2 files.
info.name: pygrib2
info.summary: Python module for reading and writing GRIB Edition 2 files.
